1. Understand the fundamentals of bionanotechnology in the context that it is the fusion between biotechnology and nanotechnology;
2. Appreciate the impact of bionanotechnology in the field of biomedical engineering;
3. Understand the key processing technologies involved in the fabrication of practical devices based on bionanotechnology.

